    "Thus, while scenario difficulty did not demonstrate a significant impact on diagnosis or treatment scores, a noteworthy relationship between diagnosis and treatment scores was unveiled.",
    "Overall, this significance implies that when there is less agreement with the diagnosis, there also tends to be less agreement with the treatment.",
